  "cooking_instructions": [
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Preheat the oven to 220°C/ 200°C (fan)/ gas 7</p><p>Peel and finely slice your <strong>brown onion[s]</strong>, then wash your<strong> spinach</strong> and pat it dry with kitchen paper</p><p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a drizzle of <strong>olive oil </strong>over a medium-high heat</p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>sliced onion</strong> and<strong> spinach</strong> and cook for 3-4 min or until the spinach is wilted and the onion has softened</p>",
      "order": 1,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-1-1670927830119-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
