          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-1-1670927830119-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, strip your <strong>mint leaves</strong> from their stems and chop them roughly, discard the stems</p><p>Chop your <strong>dill</strong> finely, including the stalks</p><p>Trim, then slice your <strong>spring onion[s]</strong></p><p>Grate your <strong>cucumber </strong>and squeeze out any excess water</p><p>Peel and finely grate your <strong>garlic</strong></p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-2-1702382444578-x200.jpg",
