    {
      "instruction": "<p>Crumble your <strong>Greek cheese</strong> into a bowl</p><p>Add the <strong>softened onion </strong>and <strong>wilted spinach</strong> to the bowl with the <strong>sliced spring onion</strong>, <strong>soft cheese</strong> and <strong>half</strong> of the <strong>chopped mint</strong> and <strong>dill</strong> (save the rest for later!)</p><p>Season with <strong>salt </strong>and <strong>pepper </strong>and<strong> </strong>give everything a good mix up – this is your <strong>spanakopita filling</strong></p>",
