    {
      "instruction": "<p>Cut your<strong> potatoes</strong> (skins on) into wedges</p><p>Add the <strong>wedges</strong> to a baking tray (or two!) with your <strong>dried oregano</strong>, a drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil </strong>and a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and<strong> pepper</strong></p><p>Give everything a good mix up and put the tray[s] in the oven for 25-30 min or until golden and crisp – these are your <strong>oregano wedges</strong></p>",
