    {
      "instruction": "<p>Dust your work surface with a generous sprinkling of <strong>flour</strong></p><p>Unwrap your <strong>puff pastry</strong> and roll it out into a rectangle shape (or two!), approx. 0.5cm thickness with a <strong>rolling pin</strong></p><p>Add the <strong>rolled pastry</strong> to a baking tray (or two!) lined with <strong>non-stick baking paper</strong>, then add the <strong>spanakopita filling</strong> to the centre of the pastry in a sausage shape leaving a 2cm border at each end</p>",
