    {
      "instruction": "<p>Cut even strips into the pastry sides, roughly 3cm wide</p><p>Tuck the top and bottom ends of the pastry over the filling, then fold the strips over the filling in a criss-cross pattern until the mixture is completely covered – this is your <strong>spanakopita</strong></p>",
