    {
      "instruction": "<p>Brush the <strong>spanakopita </strong>with<strong> </strong>a little <strong>milk </strong>and sprinkle over your <strong>toasted sesame seeds</strong></p><p>Put the tray[s] in the oven for 15-20 min or until the pastry is golden and cooked through – this is your <strong>Greek-style spanakopita</strong></p><p>Meanwhile, combine your <strong>natural</strong> <strong>yoghurt</strong> with the <strong>grated cucumber</strong>, <strong>grated garlic</strong>,<strong> </strong>the <strong>remaining chopped mint</strong> and <strong>dill </strong>and a pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and <strong>pepper </strong>– this is your <strong>herby</strong> <strong>tzatziki</strong></p>",
